OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few breaks offering some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells to end the day.
OL,8,FOften cloudy overnight with some
OL,9,Fpatchy drizzle over the hills and
OL,10,Fmountains. Frost-free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday
OL,13,Fwith further outbreaks of light
OL,14,Fdrizzle, mainly over the high ground.
OL,15,FHowever, an organised band of rain
OL,16,Flikely to arrive from the northwest by
OL,17,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
